headline: FlexJobs Announces Top 100 Companies for Hybrid Jobs in 2025
summary: FlexJobs®, the work-from-home jobs site specializing in flexible, hybrid, and remote jobs, has announced the fourth annual list of the Top 100 Companies for Hybrid Jobs. The 2025 list is based on an analysis of approximately 60,000 companies and their hybrid job posting histories in the FlexJobs database between September 1, 2024, and August 31, 2025. The featured companies are recognized for having the highest volume of hybrid job openings over the last year and are considered strong prospects
